Global Enteral Nutritional Suspension Market Insights
Enteral Nutritional Suspension Market size was valued at USD 4.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 7.2 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.2% from 2024 to 2030.

Enteral Nutritional Suspension Market Overview
The global enteral nutritional suspension market was valued at USD 7.5 billion in 2024 and is projected to expand at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.3% during the forecast period (2025-2032). This growth is driven by increasing healthcare needs, the rising prevalence of chronic diseases, and advancements in nutritional therapy. Enteral nutritional suspensions are critical for individuals with swallowing difficulties, malabsorption, and other medical conditions that impair proper nutrition. Moreover, growing awareness about personalized nutrition and the rising geriatric population are further contributing to market expansion.

